---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service | Romillie Hadeljo">
  <div class="bg-emerald-950 min-h-screen text-stone-200">
    <main class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-white mb-8 border-b border-white/10 pb-6">Terms of Service</h1>
        
        <p class="text-emerald-200/60 mb-10 text-sm">Last Updated: May 27, 2026</p>

        <div class="space-y-12">
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-emerald-400 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
            <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">By accessing and using this website, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service and all applicable laws and regulations.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-emerald-400 mb-4">2. Booking Inquiries</h2>
            <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">The inquiry form on this website is for requesting availability and pricing. Submitting an inquiry does not constitute a confirmed booking. Bookings are only confirmed once:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-stone-300 space-y-2">
              <li>Availability is verified by our team.</li>
              <li>A formal booking agreement is reached.</li>
              <li>Required deposits or payments are received.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-emerald-400 mb-4">3. House Rules</h2>
            <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">Guests are expected to follow our house rules during their stay, which include but are not limited to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-stone-300 space-y-2">
              <li>Respecting check-in and check-out times.</li>
              <li>Maintaining the property in good condition.</li>
              <li>Adhering to noise and occupancy limits.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-emerald-400 mb-4">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
            <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">All content on this website, including text, images, and logos, is the property of Romillie Hadeljo and is protected by copyright laws.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-emerald-400 mb-4">5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">Romillie Hadeljo shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising out of your use of this website or our services.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-emerald-400 mb-4">6. Governing Law</h2>
            <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">These terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the jurisdiction in which the property is located.</p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>
